  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to see a summary of my transaction **so that** I can review the details and sign to confirm it.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nFigma Design: https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=2390-502045&mode=design&t=aTiN1IeemgbJnFPl-4\r\n\r\nVisual reference:\r\n<img width=\"194\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/18485527/08301cf8-5f5f-430f-b95c-ffa51be6b886\">\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- [ ] Show title that specifies which and how many tokens you are sending, from which account and who is the reciever \r\n- [ ] Show `From` and `To` detail cards\r\n- [ ] Show `Details` card\r\n- [ ] Show `Slide to sign` slider and add authentication process\r\n- [ ] Execute transaction if the user slides and authentication succeeds\r\n- [ ] Light and dark mode should be implemented\r\n- [ ] Advanced view will be integrated in a separate issue\r\n\r\nFeel free to break up this issue in smaller issues if necessary",
